# MPSeekCommandEventType.endSeeking

**Case**

Indicates the external media player stopped seeking.

## Declaration

```swift
case endSeeking
```

## Event types

- **MPSeekCommandEventType.beginSeeking**: Indicates the external media player began seeking.
